text: Carlos Lemos (born 3 June 1988) is a Colombian sprinter. He competed in the men's 4 × 400 metres relay at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Colombian male sprinters Category:Olympic athletes of Colombia Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:South American Games bronze medalists for Colombia Category:South American Games medalists in athletics Category:Competitors at the 2014 South American Games
